pr_title: PR: Implement support for "Safdar (2018)" colour appearance model.
pr_body: Safdar (2018) is a Jzazbz model who fixed [#499](https://github.com/colour-science/colour/issues/499)

pr_title: PR: Implement support for "Zhai (2018)" colour adaptation model.
pr_body: Zhai (2018) is the colour adaptation model used for Jzazbz ([Safdar (2018)](https://github.com/colour-science/colour/pull/850))

pr_title: PR: Implement support for "Camera Sensitivities recovery Jiang (2013)".
PR: Implement support for "Kim et al. (2009)" colour appearance model.
pr_body: Kim et al. (2009) is a color appearance model that adapts the tone and color of images to different dynamic ranges for crossmedia reproduction while maintaining an appearance close to human perception.
